name: General Ledger
query:
SELECT
    `tabGeneral Ledger`.name as "General Ledger:Link/General Ledger:200",
    `tabGeneral Ledger`.account_affected as "Account Affected:Link/Account:200",
    `tabGeneral Ledger`.posting_date as "Date:Date:200",
    `tabGeneral Ledger`.credited_amount as "Cr:Currency:120",
    `tabGeneral Ledger`.debited_amount as "Dr:Currency:120",
    `tabGeneral Ledger`.account_balance as "Account Balance:Currency:200",
    `tabGeneral Ledger`.txn_type as "Particulars:Data:200",
    `tabGeneral Ledger`.txn_id as "Against:Data:200"
FROM
    `tabGeneral Ledger`
